African Women in Science and Engineering (AWSE) is an organization that seeks to increase the numbers of competent women scientists and engineers within Africa. AWSE determines to do this through various programs, spanning high schools through to the career scientist and engineer. AWSE draws its membership from all over Africa. Why Join Us How to Join Membership is open to all women in Science, Technology, Mathematics and Engineering. To join us, fill the membership form and send it to info@aawse.org.